# RunPod API key - required ONLY to run the GPU tests in gpu-tests/.
# (The on-chain verification, `npm test`, does NOT need this.)
#
# How to get one:
#   1. Sign in at https://www.runpod.io and add funds (~$10 covers the whole test suite many times over).
#   2. Go to Settings -> API Keys -> "+ API Key", create a key with read/write access.
#   3. Copy this file to `.env` and paste the key below.
#
# `.env` is git-ignored and must NEVER be committed.
RUNPOD_API_KEY=
